    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready for a new owner who appreciates a reliable ride but doesn't mind some cosmetic character. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings consistent with its age, and the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it runs well but will likely need a standard tune-up and new brake pads in the near future. It's a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable car at a reasonable price point.",
      "price": 19500.0,
